Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:48.27,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}a ja ťa odtiaľ odvediem preč.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.86,karaoke_org,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}higuraši ga naku akazu no mori de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:52.86,karaoke_sk,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Za miestom kde večer v lese plačú cikády,
